{"tid":1855619,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎既死亡率係50%，而唔係WHO所講既2%","createTime":"2020-02-01T07:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T07:56:19.000Z","uid":236109,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e60e170fe482057295cf70ff7c0cb5f380f4ed7b","tid":1855619,"uid":236109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:40:01.000Z","msg":"<ins>武漢肺炎既死亡率係50%，而唔係WHO所講既2%</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據世界衛生組織(WHO)突發衛生事件計畫執行主任瑞恩（Michael Ryan）於1月29日表示，估計武漢肺炎的死亡率為2%。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ModC1so.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModC1so.png&h=d4c9b89f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/transcripts/who-audio-script-ncov-rresser-unog-29jan2020.pdf?sfvrsn=a7158807_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fdocs%2Fdefault-source%2Fcoronaviruse%2Ftranscripts%2Fwho-audio-script-ncov-rresser-unog-29jan2020.pdf%3Fsfvrsn%3Da7158807_4&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=a7cc9173\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.who.int/docs/default-source/coronaviruse/transcripts/who-audio-script-ncov-rresser-unog-29jan2020.pdf?sfvrsn=a7158807_4</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地試下睇下WHO同埋強國所吹奏既2%死亡率係點計算出黎:<br />\n<br />\n根據2月1日Johns Hopkins University既數據:<br />\n<br />\nTotal Confirmed: 11,374<br />\nTotal Deaths: 259<br />\nTotal Recovered: 252<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JzLBxCA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJzLBxCA.png&h=67fde98c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gisanddata.maps.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/bda7594740fd40299423467b48e9ecf6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgisanddata.maps.arcgis.com%2Fapps%2Fopsdashboard%2Findex.html%23%2Fbda7594740fd40299423467b48e9ecf6&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IgvpIPIfgcH1aomtamkqoQA%3D&h=f06715d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://gisanddata.maps.arcgis.com/apps/opsdashboard/index.html#/bda7594740fd40299423467b48e9ecf6</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWHO的死亡率計算方法：<br />\n<br />\nDeath Rate<br />\n= Total Deaths / Total Confirmed<br />\n= 259 / 11,374<br />\n= 2.28%<br />\n<br />\n但懂得Statistics既人都知道咁樣既計算方法其實係玩弄數據，Total Confirmed既人數根本唔可以作為計算死亡率既Base，因為Confirmed而又未死亡or好返既人(即係仲係接受治療中既人)，我地冇辦法知道佢係將會死亡or好返，所以如果用Total Confirmed既人數做base去計Death Rate，即係假設所有接受治療中既病人會全數好返，冇一個人會死亡，咁樣計出黎個Death Rate會極低，導致大眾嚴重低估左武漢肺炎既風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>正確計算武漢肺炎既死亡率既方法應該如下:<br />\n<br />\nDeath Rate<br />\n= Total Deaths / (Total Deaths + Total Recovered)<br />\n= 259 / (259 + 252)<br />\n= 259 / 511<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">= 50.68%</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然現階段基數太細，計出黎既Death Rate只可以作為參考，但都足以證明死亡率係遠高於2%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家廣傳，切勿低估左武漢肺炎既風險。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港一定要盡快封關，阻止疫情進一步流入本港，保護本港醫護人員同埋市民。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9862900803e9b4fd617477a75f36c2b4984b2f09","tid":1855619,"uid":236109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:40:14.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a41c679f4757db901b7c6a9897d0ecbb55c52b9c","tid":1855619,"uid":236109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3a2ee9a2eb12c85d01c71742b04f280f3cdcd807","tid":1855619,"uid":236109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:40:38.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"f369c9c0c8fdb50efdaa57f3d2c544673ad3633d","tid":1855619,"uid":236109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"aa24f559a7f3a14879529b6742a2c5673cfa0926","tid":1855619,"uid":236109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T07:41:03.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"bc9b6de9aa413c86c75fe2d0e7e36a4b947b5b25","tid":1855619,"uid":9640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s